title: Gorgeous Oak Hill Landscape!
posting_body: We are nestled into the lush landscape of Austin’s Oak Hill neighborhood at the foot of Hill Country.
Minutes from downtown Austin, enjoy easy access to HWY 290 and 71, with major employers like NXP Semiconductors, Yeti, and SolarWinds nearby.
The new community offers the ultimate in convenience with a spacious co-working lounge, state-of-the-art fitness center, clubhouse with dining room, and resident package service.
Soak up the sun in one of two swimming pools or take Fido for a run at our outdoor dog park.
Contemporary finishes and modern accents including quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and soaring 10-foot-high ceilings, provide a warm, welcoming place to call home.
Surrounding greenery and mild weather create a peaceful oasis right outside your door and can be enjoyed from your private patio or yard.
We offer everything and more for the best in Austin living.
